{"tid":320114,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"只有廢柴先會俾女友check手機","createTime":"2017-07-13T09:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T18:26:08.000Z","uid":42751,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77b46a0884dfa3cbe47f93daea5dddd18f97d27f","tid":320114,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:57:17.000Z","msg":"我以前打份無前途的垃圾工嗰陣都覺得俾女友check手機無乜問題，但而家開始做到公司管理層，好多公司機密資料例如工程投標報價、內部決策響手機。<br />\n<br />\n如果俾個港女睇到呢類資料再所謂貪玩fw出去，佢地一定會勁仆街咁扮可愛咁話：我點知會搞成咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為違反公司保密協議而無咗份工都算，如果你係專業人士，嗰啲行業多數都圈子細，以後你想轉工都難，到時我真係恭喜你呀，搵著啲咁嘅閪女人<br />\n<br />\n睇見朋友俾個on9港女搞到一身蟻，事業咁就玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b092f9937ce31628863802d017ad9751e7685a","tid":320114,"uid":33001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:58:31.000Z","msg":"朋友=樓主"},{"pid":"a4942bc12a1e951471968026d08129603cd92009","tid":320114,"uid":42751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"如果你鐘意check 男友手機，搵返個一事無成的廢青做你男友啦，有事業嘅男人你高攀唔起架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b5d32b3b308d10018d735c4c2bc94f7822fa47","tid":320114,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc89d56db9ca22bd6d9eef8f44256423d9a7673","tid":320114,"uid":117752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e5f464d61f1931255f6a613871df86737ffa56","tid":320114,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:33:58.000Z","msg":"個女友on9無安全感"},{"pid":"d94c153b6f5589fd4775d949a9908e63f62e1667","tid":320114,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T18:26:08.000Z","msg":